criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Histologically confirmed prostate cancer;

          -  Intermediate-risk prostate cancer (PSA level of 10- 20 ng/mL and/or Clinical tumor
             stage ≥ T2b and/or ISUP 2 or 3, AND with risk of lymph node extension > 5% according
             to the Briganti nomogram) or high-risk prostate cancer (PSA ≥ 20 ng/mL and/or TR ≥ T2c
             and/or ISUP 4 or 5) according to d'Amico classification;

          -  Curative treatment by radical prostatectomy chosen by the multidisciplinary
             consultation meeting.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Refusal or inability to participate in the study ;

          -  Low-risk prostate cancer according to D'Amico's classification, or an
             intermediate-risk but with a risk of lymph node extension <5% according to Briganti's
             nomogram;

          -  Curative treatment other than surgical treatment chosen;

          -  Life expectancy < 12 months;

          -  Karnofsky score < 70 or ECOG score > 2.
